moji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/big/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/big/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e75d6c90eaca69f9beb3fa0461f4c122c136e314","tid":20773,"uid":39863,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-03T14:06:33.000Z","msg":"係車到瞓覺唔肯落車食飯<br />\n俾老豆打屎忽<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ef10da7410dcbfe162a7c049d8ebe80d92a2be9a","tid":20773,"uid":20943,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-03T14:07:12.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>係車到瞓覺唔肯落車食飯<br />\n俾老豆打屎忽<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 咁都要打<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 呢世未比老豆打過<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3461e7071b9e6781661692db80dc82cc60494aae","tid":20773,"uid":10241,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-03T14:12:09.000Z","msg":"細個自己落公園玩唔想帶細妹落街<br />\n襯佢換衫時自己狗衝左落公園<br />\n番到屋企比老母搵衫架打到成隻腳都係印<br />\n第二日仲要番學，比人睇到晒比人恥笑<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n搞到有童年陰影<br />\n除左校服之外唔會再著裙<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n仲有一次我老母瞓左教<br />\n我個妹係廁所玩沖涼液<br />\n咁岩比我見到，我就企左係度叫佢唔好玩<br />\n佢唔撚理我，我就on99咁一直企係度望住佢玩沖涼液整泡泡<br />\n老母瞓醒見到，比佢打到仆街<br />\n又只係打我一個，我解釋唔係我玩就話我講大話推比個妹<br />\n最後比佢搵牛皮膠紙封口，尼龍繩綁手腳<br />\n跪地跪左成日，由晏就跪到夜晚瞓教<br />\n連飯都沒得食<br />\n自此我就好撚憎我個妹<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n大個同老母提起依件事，佢竟然話我發夢記錯<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" cla