>\n跪地跪左成日，由晏就跪到夜晚瞓教<br />\n連飯都沒得食<br />\n自此我就好撚憎我個妹<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n大個同老母提起依件事，佢竟然話我發夢記錯<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\nSM<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n屌 變晒sosad<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c63e32378421b2ca855bbdb9f593091cb4715e4b","tid":20773,"uid":10241,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-03T14:21:44.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>細個自己落公園玩唔想帶細妹落街<br />\n襯佢換衫時自己狗衝左落公園<br />\n番到屋企比老母搵衫架打到成隻腳都係印<br />\n第二日仲要番學，比人睇到晒比人恥笑<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n搞到有童年陰影<br />\n除左校服之外唔會再著裙<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n仲有一次我老母瞓左教<br />\n我個妹係廁所玩沖涼液<br />\n咁岩比我見到，我就企左係度叫佢唔好玩<br />\n佢唔撚理我，我就on99咁一直企係度望住佢玩沖涼液整泡泡<br />\n老母瞓醒見到，比佢打到仆街<br />\n又只係打我一個，我解釋唔係我玩就話我講大話推比個妹<br />\n最後比佢搵<span style=\"color: red;\">牛皮膠紙封口，尼龍繩綁手腳</span><br />\n跪地跪左成日，由晏就跪到夜晚瞓教<br />\n連飯都沒得食<br />\n自此我就好撚憎我個妹<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n大個同老母提起依件事，佢竟然話我發夢記錯<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\nSM<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n依家又唔見佢咁對自己個孫女<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n連搵滕條打下都沒...<br />\n年紀越大越仁慈<br />\n令我懷疑佢係咪好憎我<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n我比佢搞到又有童年陰影<br />\n由細到大都唔戴口罩同手鏈腳鏈果堆<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2e8a3528ed3a86dd03d1aafc5c7e51b3b08f4d77","tid":20773,"uid":29126,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-03T14:24:28.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"cf0c7f710bb4984df1bfeac7cab0ce16d80d9644","tid":20773,"uid":4854,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-03T14:28:38.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>老母係肥婆 有一日忍唔著屌左句: 死肥婆賣菠蘿啦 <br />\n比佢當大陸虐狗個啲咁打<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/big/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"